{"tid":445533,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8滯銷　內地零售商最多劈近800人仔 (19:42)","createTime":"2017-10-23T12:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T03:23:08.000Z","uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8fad539d2d3ebdf7929c7d537cb3f57cc27fc4","tid":445533,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=78JB%2BGYRbRxacVZBcvZYcQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=33e8f648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內媒報道，iPhone 8/8 Plus在開售之初表現平平，不僅沒有出現了大排長龍、加價炒賣的情況，甚至在首發日就出現破發現象(零售價較官方價便宜200元人民幣)；而最新消息指，上述慘淡銷情僅僅是開端，目前iPhone 8國行版在內地第三方平台報價下跌達400至逾800元人民幣(下同)不等。<br />\n　　<br />\n在內地，某大電商最近舉行的iPhone 8活動也上，已經明確列出不同型號的iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus價格，均遠低於蘋果官方售價，減價最厲害的是iPhone 8 64GB金色版，原價5888元，目前只要4999元就可以帶回家，減價高達889元，像iPhone 8 Plus就全線一律減價400元。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說零售商網站顯示要立即搶購，但點擊進去就發現基本上都有貨，完全不需要搶購，可以說是大家連搶都懶得搶了。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘋果已經不再公布新品首發一周的銷量，而從第三方報告以及減價頻率來看，可以說iPhone 8/8 Plus銷售狀況之差遠超蘋果的想像。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171023/20171023194210fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171023%2F20171023194210fi.html&d=78JB%2BGYRbRxacVZBcvZYcQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cbe9106e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171023/20171023194210fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"68a4c688ea7b2a26755dae08356d24a9a35ddfaf","tid":445533,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:58:49.000Z","msg":"個個等X<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9735daa6d137afb4d76398a401212930fd08a4f","tid":445533,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"個個想要X"},{"pid":"fbbeaa04cd3eebd5972e4bab56bd6082549e0fd2","tid":445533,"uid":65144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"部8咪鬼出好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.g